'''印度料理'''是由[[印度次大陆|印度次大陆]]原生各种传统及地方性料理组成的。视乎气候、土地、文化和族群的不同，其内容形式多变，常用当地的调料和药材蔬果。印度料理亦深受次大陆以[[印度教|印度教]]为首的宗教及其它文化习俗影响。[[莫卧儿帝国|莫卧儿帝国]]等伊斯兰政权也对印度料理有所贡献和改变，如[[印度咖喱角|萨莫萨三角饺]]及[[抓饭|抓饭]]。<ref>{{cite book|author=Dias|title=Steward, The|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SRx9I2BqSpMC&pg=PA215|year=1996|publisher=Orient Blackswan|isbn=978-81-250-0325-0|page=215|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107064735/https://books.google.com/books?id=SRx9I2BqSpMC&pg=PA215|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GestelandGesteland2010">{{cite book|last1=Gesteland|first1=Richard R.|last2=Gesteland|first2=Mary C.|title=India: Cross-cultural Business Behavior : for Business People, Expatriates and Scholars|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tXqDRS4IN1IC|year=2010|publisher=Copenhagen Business School Press DK|isbn=978-87-630-0222-6|page=176|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2013-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528060247/http://books.google.com/books?id=tXqDRS4IN1IC|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[贸易|贸易]]、[[战争|战争]]和[[殖民主义|殖民]]带给印度一部分新食物，得益于哥伦布发现美洲，[[马铃薯|马铃薯]]、[[番茄|番茄]]、[[辣椒|辣椒]]、[[花生|花生]]和[[番石榴|番石榴]]成了印度不少地方的主要作物。在历史上，国际关系也塑造了印度料理，如与欧洲间的香料生意促成了[[地理大发现|地理大发现]]。當时香料多在印度采购集散，在欧亞大陆各处贩卖。印度料理亦施影响于全球烹饪，特别是环印度洋、中东、中北美地区。在和印度料理交流较深的欧洲料理中，尤以印度旧宗主英国料理所含印度因素为多。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/seta/2008/10/16/stories/2008101650731500.htm|work=The Hindu|accessdate=26 June 2012|title=Potato: historically important vegetable|date=16 October 2008|first=D|last=Balasubramanian|location=Chennai, India|archive-date=2008-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081020053402/http://www.hindu.com/seta/2008/10/16/stories/2008101650731500.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="cornillez1999">{{cite web|title=The History of the Spice Trade in India|url=http://www.english.emory.edu/Bahri/Spice_Trade.html|date=Spring 1999|last=Cornillez|first=Louise Marie M.|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-date=2012-10-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B95O9T3p?url=http://www.english.emory.edu/Bahri/Spice_Trade.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="vegvoyages.com">{{cite web|title=Nasi, Kari, Biryani & Mee|url=http://www.vegvoyages.com/food.htm|accessdate=23 June 2009|publisher=Veg Voyages|archive-date=2009-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090628154725/http://www.vegvoyages.com/food.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Asia Food Features|url=http://www.asiafood.org/features_dietary_culture4.cfm|accessdate=23 June 2009|publisher=Asiafood.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010525095845/http://www.asiafood.org/features_dietary_culture4.cfm|archive-date=2001-05-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
印度料理体现了8000年以来各族群和文化在次大陆上交融碰撞的[[印度历史|历史]]，现代印度料理中的多变口味和乡土料理就是从这个历史中成长出来的。后来，和葡萄牙及英国的贸易关系又为已十分多元的印度料理添砖加瓦。<ref name="Dubey2011">{{cite book|author=Krishna Gopal Dubey|title=The Indian Cuisine|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_xiwkbgJbSQC|year=2011|publisher=PHI Learning Pvt. Ltd.|isbn=978-81-203-4170-8|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107064736/https://books.google.com/books?id=_xiwkbgJbSQC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Achaya">{{cite book|author=K T Achaya|title=The Story of Our Food|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bk9RHRCqZOkC|year=2003|publisher=Universities Press|isbn=9788173712937|access-date=2020-07-12|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107064737/https://books.google.com/books?id=bk9RHRCqZOkC|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 原料 ==
[[File:3_types_of_lentil.jpg|左]]
印度料理的主食包括稻米、小麦、珍珠粟（{{Lang-hi|बाजरा|translit=bājra}}），以及豆類，如小扁豆（{{Lang-hi|मसूर|translit=masoor}}）、[[木豆|木豆]]（{{Lang-hi|अरहर|translit=arahar}}）、[[黑豆|黑小豆]]（{{Lang-hi|उड़द|translit=uṛad}}）、[[绿豆|绿豆]]（{{Lang-hi|मूँग|translit=moong}}）。这些豆子有的被剥去豆荚，有的连[[珠被|种皮]]也剥去，这种被{{Internal link helper/en|剥去种皮的豆子|dal}}可以直接烹饪无需泡发，应用很广，多被做成豆糊或豆汤。一些荚豆，如[[鹰嘴豆|鹰嘴豆]]、[[菜豆|芸豆]]和{{Internal link helper/en|黑眼豆|black-eyed pea}}也十分常见（特别是[[北印度|北印度]]）。鹰嘴豆和绿豆也会被制成{{Internal link helper/en|豆粉|besan}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How Do I Cook Red Split Lentils from Real Foods|url=https://www.realfoods.co.uk/article/how-do-i-cook-red-split-lentils|accessdate=2020-07-12|last=Foods 2015|first=Real|work=www.realfoods.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111170300/https://www.realfoods.co.uk/article/how-do-i-cook-red-split-lentils|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref name="Johnston1958">{{cite book|first=Bruce F.|last=Johnston|title=The Staple Food Economies of Western Tropical Africa|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wyCrAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA14|year=1958|publisher=Stanford University Press|isbn=978-0-8047-0537-0|page=14|access-date=2021-03-04|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905190111/https://books.google.com/books?id=wyCrAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

不少印度料理用植物油烹饪，其中西、北印度多用[[花生油|花生油]]，印度东部多用[[芥菜籽|芥子]]油<ref name="LocricchioMcConnell2004">{{cite book|first1=Matthew|last1=Locricchio|first2=Jack|last2=McConnell|title=The Cooking of India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ijiRROaS3UUC&pg=PA77|year=2004|publisher=Marshall Cavendish|isbn=978-0-7614-1730-9|page=77|access-date=2021-03-04|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905190117/https://books.google.com/books?id=ijiRROaS3UUC&pg=PA77|dead-url=no}}</ref>，印度最南端的[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]和[[泰米尔纳德邦|泰米尔纳德邦]]流行[[椰子油|椰子油]]。<ref name="Seshadri2007">{{cite book|first=Diana|last=Seshadri|title=Food for The Gods|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1GWPUkI_xQsC&pg=PA35|year=2007|publisher=Lulu.com|isbn=978-1-4303-1269-7|page=35|access-date=2021-03-04|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905190124/https://books.google.com/books?id=1GWPUkI_xQsC&pg=PA35|dead-url=no}}{{self-published source|date=February 2020}}</ref> 因芝麻油有强烈的坚果香气，故在[[南印度|南印度]]很常见<ref name="ShiHo2010">{{cite book|first1=John|last1=Shi|author2=Chi-Tang Ho|first3=Fereidoon|last3=Shahidi|title=Functional Foods of the East|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7VENd7fgLIkC&pg=PA64|year=2010|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-1-4200-7192-4|page=64|access-date=2021-03-04|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905190128/https://books.google.com/books?id=7VENd7fgLIkC&pg=PA64|dead-url=no}}</ref> 21世纪以来，[[葵花籽油|葵花籽油]]、[[棉籽油|棉籽油]]、[[红花|红花]]籽油和[[大豆油|大豆油]]也在印度逐渐兴起<ref name="KumarDubey2006">{{cite book|first1=Arvind|last1=Kumar|first2=Pushpalata|last2=Dubey|title=Green Technologies for Sustainable Agriculture|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rrZIde3mIlQC&pg=PA28|year=2006|publisher=Daya Publishing House|isbn=978-81-7035-419-2|page=28|access-date=2021-03-04|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905190144/https://books.google.com/books?id=rrZIde3mIlQC&pg=PA28|dead-url=no}}</ref>替代[[黄油|黄油]]的[[氫化脂肪|氢化植物油]]也开始流行<ref name="Sharma">{{cite book|author=Dr. J. P. Sharma|title=Academic Biology IX|year=2008|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HZBLu-IGByQC&pg=PA97|publisher=Laxmi Publications|isbn=978-81-7008-579-9|page=97|access-date=2021-03-04|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920140637/https://books.google.com/books?id=HZBLu-IGByQC&pg=PA97|dead-url=no}}</ref>

